{
  "stem": "5103.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, on the cart, on the mattress, and my father pushing, my mother walking behind.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother looked pretty thin, even though we had had something to eat there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But my mother looked still fairly thin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so I don't think they took too much notice of us somehow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We looked a bit bedraggled looking, and we didn't look like anything that was-- and also, because we had a cart.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We just weren't walking, we had some belongings on it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we eventually had to cross a bridge, where there was a guard.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were like army personnel standing there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and my father had said, look, all these papers, I've got, so don't worry, and just-- just, you know, look at them straight in the face.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Look-- just look.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother had blue eyes, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But my mother's hair was a little darker.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- but he said to me, [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Corrie, ?] when they look at you, or they say anything, just smile.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Laugh, laugh.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we got to do the bridge, and there was a whole lot-- in that Haarlemmermeer, where we were going, there was the food stores were being-- like, there were stores from the farmers, where they had, like, big storage area where they-- the-- the army also used to come and take their food from.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So there was a lot of transport going across that bridge, and they were checking regularly-- checkpoint there.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
